	<a name=3D"procedure"></a>
	<h6>SPSS Statistics</h6>
	<h2><strong>SPSS Statistics procedure</strong> to carry out a Wilcoxon sig=
ned-rank test</h2>
=09
	<p>The six steps below show you how to analyse your data using a Wilcoxon =
signed-rank test in SPSS Statistics. At the end of these six steps, we show=
 you how to interpret the results from this test.</p>
=09
	<p class=3D"note"><span class=3D"note-title">Note 1:</span> We show you th=
e <strong>Legacy Dialogs &gt; 2 Related Samples</strong> procedure in SPSS =
